show.description: When betrayed by her best friend Shivani and husband Lalit, Dhvani dies, only to wake up six months in the past with one chance to rewrite her fate. Armed with vengeance and cunning, she exposes lies, confronts Yakshit, and turns the deadly game of love and betrayal on its head. Watch Now!
